BEGIN DSJOB
   Identifier "IdsProvDEAFkey"
   DateModified "2023-05-10"
   TimeModified "00.28.16"
   BEGIN DSRECORD
      Identifier "ROOT"
      OLEType "CJobDefn"
      Readonly "0"
      Name "IdsProvDEAFkey"
      Description "IDS Provider DEA  Data Foreign Keying.  "
      NextID "5"
      Container "V0"
      FullDescription =+=+=+=
COPYRIGHT 2004 BLUE CROSS/BLUE SHIELD OF KANSAS CITY 


JOB NAME:     IdsProvDEAFkey

DESCRIPTION:     Takes the sorted file and applies the Foreign key.  
      

INPUTS:  File from IdsProvDEAPkey
	
  
HASH FILES:     hf_recycle - contains records that had errors on them for recycle.  Recycle is not used in this program - file is completely updated from Facets each time.


TRANSFORMS:  GetFkeyCodes 
                                 
                           Unknown and Not Applicable rows are created - all rows are sent through collector to combine into output file
                           

PROCESSING:  This job would be run whenever there is an update to the NDC table/file.  Until now, we got the NDC (National Drug Code) file from CRMS, but now are looking for a 
  different source.  When this source is located and we get new files, these jobs will probably need to be re-written.

OUTPUTS:  File for PROV_DEA table

MODIFICATIONS:
            BJ Luce        08/2004         -   Originally Programmed
            Brent Leland 09/20/2004    -  Added link partioner.
            Steph Goddard  06/01/2005  changed for sequencer

Developer                  Date                 Project/Altiris #      Change Description                                                            Development Project      Code Reviewer          Date Reviewed       
------------------              --------------------     ------------------------      -----------------------------------------------------------------------                       --------------------------------       -------------------------------   ----------------------------       
Kalyan Neelam         2009-10-28            TTR-525         Added new fields CLM_TRANS_ADD_IN, ADDR_LN2,             devlIDS                      Steph Goddard        10/29/2009
                                                                                      NTNL_PROV_ID, NTNL_PROV_ID_SPEC_DESC                                                           

Manasa Andru         2014-03-14           TFS - 4011      Updated the fields EFF_DT_SK and TERM_DT_SK               IntegrateCurDevl              Kalyan Neelam            2014-03-20
                                                                                   as per the mapping rules in the ForeignKey1 transformer.
Kalyan Neelam        2015-10-30      5403/TFS1048     Added 2 new columns on end -                                                 IntegrateDev1              Bhoomi Dasari           11/9/2015
                                                                                 NTNL_PROV_ID_PROV_TYP_DESC and NTNL_PROV_ID_PROV_TYP_DESC

Ravi Abburi             2018-01-29    5781 - HEDIS            Added the NTNL_PROV_SK                                               IntegrateDev2                   Kalyan Neelam            2018-04-19





















